reviewText: ​I liked the overal course and the info! the ONLY MAJOR PROBLEM was that I had to literally beg for my assignment to be corrected ! if that is adressed it will be a better course

Great introductory overview.  10-hour length is just what I was looking for.  I learned a lot of terminology and fundamental concepts in digital marketing - just enough to figure out where I want to go into more depth.  For my needs, this was totally sufficient and much more efficient than taking a 30-hour class.  Also appreciated that the material was current - as far as I can tell, this course was produced in 2021.  Thank you UC Irvine and Coursera!

Thank you! I want to express my gratitude to the teachers who made such a useful and necessary course. The development of information systems has an impact on all areas of the economy and especially on marketing.
The course is very detailed and helpful to learn basics.
I have learnt so much from this course!

The course is useful and informative. The instructor gave detailed information about the statics, research and case study. I highly recommend this course to people who want to learn fundamentals of digital marketing in the most simple way.

it was very informative and beneficial
